3d","type":"paragraph","text":"为不是实事求是研究问题而是狂要自大夸夸其谈","index":37,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"3e5b1f24a2"},{"id":"80e4ce1062","type":"paragraph","text":"戒律太多","index":38,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"3e5b1f24a2"},{"id":"d01d3332ea","type":"paragraph","text":"的文章不应允许出来争吗。有人认为讨论问题态","index":39,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"3e5b1f24a2"},{"id":"c65c5bd1d1","type":"paragraph","text":"度不好的文章不应允许争鸣。有人把这些问题归","index":40,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"3e5b1f24a2"},{"id":"3144ad21c7","type":"paragraph","text":"结为“百家争鸣”与“学风”问题。","index":41,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"3e5b1f24a2"},{"id":"2474e7499a","type":"paragraph","text":"五、哲学家提出唯心主义的评价问题，哲学","index":42,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"3e5b1f24a2"},{"id":"90a5790d3f","type":"paragraph","text":"遗产的继承性问题。这个问题带有普遍性，文学","index":43,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"3e5b1f24a2"},{"id":"62a007ad8e","type":"paragraph","text":"界、法学界都在讨论这个问题。要不要研究资产","index":44,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"3e5b1f24a2"},{"id":"06a65b9499","type":"paragraph","text":"阶级社会学中那些对我们有用的问题也已经提","index":45,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"3e5b1f24a2"},{"id":"d6b01f0315","type":"paragraph","text":"出。目前在社会科学中几个理论性最强的方面","index":46,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"3e5b1f24a2"},{"id":"1d595636c2","type":"paragraph","text":"（如辩证唯物主义与历史唯物主义、政治经济学","index":47,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"3e5b1f24a2"},{"id":"066b066e8f","type":"paragraph","text":"等）中怎样进行研究的问题也未解决。","index":48,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"3e5b1f24a2"},{"id":"5083c33d1a","type":"paragraph","text":"目前不要去","index":49,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"3e5b1f24a2"},{"id":"37c27c8f6c","type":"paragraph","text":"六、目前文艺界一方面“左”的教条主义、找主要危险，宗派主义倾向仍然很严重，另一方面资产阶级、而应按具体问小资产阶级思想又确实有些拾头。哪一方面是主题处理","index":50,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"3e5b1f24a2"},{"id":"b358460dc1","type":"paragraph","text":"要危险，在一些同志中间看法不一致。对这种状","index":51,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"3e5b1f24a2"},{"id":"848b1ea23f","type":"paragraph","text":"况，应该怎样估计？","index":52,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"3e5b1f24a2"},{"id":"f8bc81df22","type":"paragraph","text":"七、在文学作品中应该如何反映人民内部的","index":53,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"3e5b1f24a2"},{"id":"89c9c92ae4","type":"paragraph","text":"矛盾，揭露和批评生活中的缺点，应当注意什么","index":54,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"3e5b1f24a2"},{"id":"f8774cbde5","type":"paragraph","text":"原则，如何掌握分寸？","index":55,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"3e5b1f24a2"},{"id":"0fdc2af814","type":"paragraph","text":"不对。但可","index":56,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"3e5b1f24a2"},{"id":"7d5a1b334d","type":"paragraph","text":"八、目前有些作家认为文学的目的就是写真以充许少数人实，因此，“看到什么就写什么”，“感受即真这样做","index":57,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"3e5b1f24a2"},{"id":"88495f57d4","type":"paragraph","text":"实”，至于作品对人民有什么教育作用，作家用","index":58,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"3e5b1f24a2"},{"id":"f6090f2e2d","type":"paragraph","text":"不着考虑。对于文学的真实性与思想性的关系，","index":59,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"3e5b1f24a2"},{"id":"f228e83cf5","type":"paragraph","text":"应该怎样看？","index":60,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"3e5b1f24a2"},{"id":"b2487a8409","type":"paragraph","text":"九、关于社会主义现实主义问题，在文艺界","index":61,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"3e5b1f24a2"},{"id":"977b97aa95","type":"paragraph","text":"看法不一致。有些人认为文学既然是反映现实，","index":62,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"3e5b1f24a2"},{"id":"664bad7e28","type":"paragraph","text":"只要现实主义就够了，现实主义到了社会主义革","index":63,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"3e5b1f24a2"},{"id":"68da926be3","type":"paragraph","text":"命时代当然就成了社会主义革命时代的现实主","index":64,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"3e5b1f24a2"},{"id":"90152a40ea","type":"paragraph","text":"义，没有什么社会主义现实主义。有些人认为作","index":65,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"3e5b1f24a2"},{"id":"e9d47e5803","type":"paragraph","text":"家反映现实离不开他的立场观点，具有社会主义","index":66,"publicationI